1.description: Thou must scan all client-side JavaScript for exposed API Keys (Supabase, AWS, Firebase).

3.description: Thou must query for 'post_edits', 'audit_logs', and 'deleted_at' columns to recover hidden history.

4.name: The Unity of Being

5.name: The Weighing of Scales
5.description: If financial transactions exist, Thou must simulate slippage to detect value extraction.

6.name: The Duality of Records
